CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "Promenade - Nothing like a stroll down the Avenue on Easter Sunday. Misses Myrna Aiken and Rosemarie Lawrence turn on the personality as they brighten Centre Avenue.-Harris Photo
TitMainTitle: Myrna Aiken and Rosemarie Lawrence, wearing tailored suits and hats, walking along on sidewalk on Centre Avenue by the Falk School, University of Pittsburgh, another version
